Show Summary: A crime documentary series. North Woods Law follows Maines
elite Game Wardens as they navigate the Pine Tree States rugged terrain
and twisted back roads. Each punch of the time clock is a ticket to
extreme danger and drama as undercover stings and intense rescues are
all in a days work. Whether they are tracking bears on dangerous
mountains or busting drunk drivers on ATVs, the Maine Game Wardens risk
life and limb to protect animals and serve the people of Maine.
